---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base title="N9 Mirror — MeeGo Harmattan Repository" active="home">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-6 py-20 md:px-10 md:py-28 lg:px-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wider text-n9-400">
        Community archive
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
        MeeGo Harmattan, still alive.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg font-medium text-n9-300 md:text-xl">
        A mirror of the original Nokia developer repositories and community tools
        for the Nokia N9. Keeping the swipe alive.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a
          href="/setup"
          class="flex h-11 items-center rounded-md bg-n9-100 px-5 text-sm font-medium text-n9-900 transition hover:bg-white"
        >
          Add the mirror
        </a>
        <a
          href="/browse"
          class="flex h-11 items-center rounded-md border border-n9-700 bg-n9-800 px-5 text-sm font-medium text-n9-100 transition hover:border-n9-500"
        >
          Browse archive
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl border-t border-n9-800 px-6 py-20 md:px-10 lg:px-16">
    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
      <a
        href="/setup"
        class="group rounded-lg border border-n9-700 bg-n9-800 p-6 transition hover:border-n9-500"
      >
        <div class="mb-4 text-3xl">⚙️</div>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Setup</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-n9-300">
          Add the mirror to your N9 — one-line install or manual sources.list.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-n9-200 group-hover:text-white">
          Get started →
        </p>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/browse"
        class="group rounded-lg border border-n9-700 bg-n9-800 p-6 transition hover:border-n9-500"
      >
        <div class="mb-4 text-3xl">📦</div>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Browse</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-n9-300">
          Explore the full mirror — SDK packages, Nokia binaries, firmware, tools.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-n9-200 group-hover:text-white">
          Open browser →
        </p>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/docs/"
        class="group rounded-lg border border-n9-700 bg-n9-800 p-6 transition hover:border-n9-500"
      >
        <div class="mb-4 text-3xl">📖</div>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Docs</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-n9-300">
          The original Nokia Harmattan developer documentation, mirrored intact.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-n9-200 group-hover:text-white">
          Open docs →
        </p>
      </a>

      <a
        href="/guides/"
        class="group rounded-lg border border-n9-700 bg-n9-800 p-6 transition hover:border-n9-500"
      >
        <div class="mb-4 text-3xl">📚</div>
        <h2 class="mb-2 text-xl font-semibold text-white">Guides</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-n9-300">
          Step-by-step tutorials — developer mode, app installation, and more.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm font-medium text-n9-200 group-hover:text-white">
          Read guides →
        </p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl border-t border-n9-800 px-6 py-20 md:px-10 lg:px-16">
    <div class="grid gap-12 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Why this exists</h2>
        <p class="text-base text-n9-300 leading-relaxed">
          The original Nokia repositories at <code class="rounded bg-n9-800 px-1.5 py-0.5 text-sm">harmattan-dev.nokia.com</code> went
          offline years ago. This is a community mirror, served from
          Cloudflare R2, free for anyone who still loves their N9.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold text-white">What's mirrored</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-base text-n9-300">
          <li>• Harmattan SDK (free, non-free, source)</li>
          <li>• Nokia binary packages</li>
          <li>• N9 community flat repos (001, apps, tools)</li>
          <li>• Firmware images and flashing tools</li>
          <li>• The original Harmattan developer documentation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
